Package: ciflyr
Title: Flexible Reachability Framework for Causal Inference
Version: 0.1.0
Maintainer: Marcel Wienöbst <marcel.wienoebst@gmx.de>
Author: Marcel Wienöbst [aut, cre]
Authors@R: 
    person("Marcel", "Wienöbst", , "marcel.wienoebst@gmx.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a framework for writing flexible linear-time reachability-based algorithms for graphical causal inference. Rule tables are used to encode to customize the reachability algorithm to typical tasks in causal inference such as finding d-connected nodes or more advanced applications.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
